# 5. メンバーを探そう！

Tsukasa: Uh!
Emu: He's awake! Tsukasa, are you okay?
Tsukasa: I passed out? That's right, it was all but a dream. There's no way that weird world, with the weird Miku, and a weird talking stuffed animal would be rea—
Miku: Are you feeling okay?
Bunny Plushie: Does your head hurt?
Tsukasa: It wasn't a dream?!
Tsukasa: This is crazy... Why is this happening to me!
KAITO: Well, this is a problem... He's not in a state where we can try to uncover his true feelings.
Tsukasa: I've had enough, I'm leaving! If that “Untitled” song got me here, stopping it should take me back, right?
Tsukasa: Wait a second, where's my phone... It's gone! As if things weren't bad enough...
Tsukasa: Aaargh! I'll do anything you want, but please release me! I'm losing my mind here!
Emu: Aaanything?
Emu: Then will you perform with me as a cast member at the Wonder Stage?
Tsukasa: If that's what I must do to get out of here, yes!
Emu: Yay! It's a promise, right? Okay, I'll help you find your phone!
Emu: Where could it be... I see it! It's hanging from a branch over there!
Tsukasa: What, really? That was quick!
Emu: I have the eyes of a hawk! I'll go and get it for you. Whew! Here it is!
Tsukasa: Good job, Emu! Now I just have to stop “Untitled” and I'll be out of here!
Miku: Hey, don't go yet!
Tsukasa: Ngh... Where am I? Yes! It's the run-down stage from earlier!
Tsukasa: I did it! I escaped from that nightmare!
Emu: I had a great time in that world!
Emu: Let's make shows that are as fun as that place!
Tsukasa: Leave it to me! No, wait.
Tsukasa: Why are you roping me into your shows?
Emu: What do you mean? You said you'd do anything to get back and I helped you.
Tsukasa: Um... Did I say that? I-I don't seem to recall... Wasn't it all a dream anyway?
Emu: But you promised...
Tsukasa: Uh...
Mascot: Gotcha! How dare you kidnap Miss Emu!
Tsukasa: K-Kidnap?!
Mascot: Don't try to deny it! I have video evidence on my hidden camera! You blinded me and young miss with your phone and abducted her!
Tsukasa: That's preposterous, I didn't do that! And why would a park mascot have a hidden camera?!
Mascot: That's irrelevant! You realized your mistake and brought young miss back, but what you did is still a crime!
Tsukasa: Ugh! It hurts! Stop!
Tsukasa: (What did I get myself into this time? Kidnapping? Miss? Why's this guy so deferential towards her anyway?)
Emu: No fighting!
Emu: Tsukasa is my very special friend, who's going to do shows with me! Shows that everyone will love!
Emu: So be nice to each other!
Mascot: *freeze*
Mascot: Is that true? You'll be working on this stage with young miss Emu?
Tsukasa: It's um, complicated...
Mascot: *grips harder*
Tsukasa: (Urgh... How come this mascot's so strong?! Is he going to crush the life out of me if I give the wrong answer?)
Mascot: I asked you if you're going to do shows with young miss Emu.
Tsukasa: Y-Yes! That's right! Emu and I will perform here together!
Mascot: Are you telling the truth?
Tsukasa: Eek! Y-Yes, absolutely, pinky swear!
Emu: Yay! Woohoo!
Tsukasa: *Cough*... *Cough*... This is coercion, you know...
Emu: Thank you sooo much, Tsukasa! I'm so happy!
Emu: Teehee! What will our first show be? Oh, can we make it about life among the stars?
Tsukasa: Sigh... I have no choice now, do I...
Tsukasa: Hmm... But this could make for a compelling origin story. Setting out on my path to stardom amongst overwhelming difficulties... Yes, I should stay positive!
Tsukasa: Okay, if I'm doing this, I'm going to make it a show worthy of the world's top star-to-be!
Emu: Yup yup! Let's make it a fun-tastic magical experience!
Tsukasa: Before we can begin, we need to recruit more members for our troupe.
Emu: The two of us aren't enough?
Tsukasa: Even including Mr. Mascot here we only have a cast of three. That's not enough for a proper show.
Emu: I see! The more the merrier, right? Let's go and find more members!
Tsukasa: Easier said than done... How do we find people who'd like to join us?
Emu: Look, Tsukasa! Tiny robots!
Tsukasa: Robots? Are you lost in your fantasies again? Oh... You weren't kidding...
???: Hehe. My little darlings are all very energized today. Why? Because we'll be putting on a show here!
???: My dear mechanical actors, it's showtime!
Tsukasa: What am I even looking at?!
